One of your uncles
was in the service?

00:02:23.580 --> 00:02:27.230
You don't know what service it was?

00:02:27.230 --> 00:02:28.530
Yes, ma'am.

00:02:28.530 --> 00:02:30.270
[ Inaudible Comment ]

00:02:30.270 --> 00:02:32.530
She's in the Navy?

00:02:32.530 --> 00:02:33.830
Your uncle?

00:02:33.830 --> 00:02:37.000
Do you know what service he was in?

00:02:37.000 --> 00:02:39.470
The Army. I'm an Army veteran,

00:02:39.470 --> 00:02:41.540
