00:07:07.130 --> 00:07:12.120
and on those stamps it
features the Congressional Medal

00:07:12.120 --> 00:07:16.000
of Honor, very unique opportunity.

00:07:16.000 --> 00:07:21.660
And Brian was one of ten
veterans who was at that service

00:07:21.660 --> 00:07:24.720
and I believe who spoke,
at least to the media,

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:29.210
