00:34:11.230 --> 00:34:13.340
That's a good question.

00:34:13.340 --> 00:34:16.910
I didn't volunteer for this award.

00:34:16.910 --> 00:34:20.950
I didn't put in an application.

00:34:25.130 --> 00:34:28.370
As one of my colleagues and
