00:34:49.000 --> 00:34:52.060
They thought you were worthy of it.

00:34:53.960 --> 00:34:57.620
I'm not sure that I am.

00:34:57.620 --> 00:35:01.600
And that's not a winner.

00:35:03.170 --> 00:35:06.280
A winner is something that
