00:35:06.280 --> 00:35:08.970
And I didn't work to get this.

00:35:13.160 --> 00:35:16.390
Did that answer the question?

00:35:16.390 --> 00:35:17.690
&gt;&gt; Yes.

00:35:17.690 --> 00:35:18.990
&gt;&gt; Brian Thacker: Sort of?

00:35:18.990 --> 00:35:20.290
&gt;&gt; Yes.

